msgid "Signed distance field global illumination (SDFGI)"
msgstr "Soilsiú domhanda réimse achair sínithe (SDFGI)"

msgid ""
"Signed distance field global illumination (SDFGI) is a novel technique "
"available in Godot 4.0. It provides semi-real-time global illumination that "
"scales to any world size and works with procedurally generated levels."
msgstr ""
"Teicníc úrnua atá ar fáil in Godot 4.0 is ea soilsiú domhanda an achair "
"sínithe (SDFGI). Soláthraíonn sé soilsiú domhanda leathfhíor-ama a scálaíonn "
"go haon mhéid dhomhanda agus a oibríonn le leibhéil a ghintear de réir nós "
"imeachta."

msgid ""
"SDFGI supports dynamic lights, but *not* dynamic occluders or dynamic "
"emissive surfaces. Therefore, SDFGI provides better real-time ability "
"than :ref:`baked lightmaps <doc_using_lightmap_gi>`, but worse real-time "
"ability than :ref:`VoxelGI <doc_using_voxel_gi>`."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn SDFGI le soilse dinimiciúla, ach * ní * occluders dinimiciúil nó "
"dromchlaí dinimiciúil emissive. Dá bhrí sin, soláthraíonn SDFGI cumas fíor-"
"ama níos fearr ná :ref:`léarscáileanna bácáilte <doc_using_lightmap_gi>`, "
"ach cumas fíor-ama níos measa ná :ref:`VoxelGI <doc_using_voxel_gi>`."

msgid ""
"From a performance standpoint, SDFGI is one of the most demanding global "
"illumination techniques in Godot. Like with VoxelGI, there are still many "
"settings available to tweak its performance requirements at the cost of "
"quality."
msgstr ""
"Ó thaobh feidhmíochta, tá SDFGI ar cheann de na teicnící soilsithe domhanda "
"is déine i Godot. Cosúil le VoxelGI, tá go leor socruithe ar fáil fós chun a "
"riachtanais feidhmíochta a thaispeáint ar chostas cáilíochta."

msgid ""
"Not sure if SDFGI is suited to your needs? "
"See :ref:`doc_introduction_to_global_illumination_comparison` for a "
"comparison of GI techniques available in Godot 4."
msgstr ""
"Níl tú cinnte an bhfuil SDFGI oiriúnach le do riachtanais? Féach:ref: "
"`doc_introduction_to_global_illumination_comparison` le haghaidh comparáid a "
"dhéanamh ar theicnící GI atá ar fáil i Godot 4."

msgid "Visual comparison"
msgstr "Comparáid amhairc"

msgid "SDFGI disabled."
msgstr "SDFGI faoi mhíchumas."

