msgid "Setting up SDFGI"
msgstr "SDFGI a bhunú"

msgid ""
"In Godot, SDFGI is the global illumination technique with the fewest "
"required steps to enable:"
msgstr ""
"I Godot, is é SDFGI an teicníc soilsithe domhanda leis an gcéimeanna is lú "
"riachtanacha chun:"

msgid ""
"Make sure your MeshInstance nodes have their **Global Illumination > Mode** "
"property set to **Static** in the inspector."
msgstr ""
"Cinntigh go bhfuil an t-airí **Global Illumination> Mode** ar do nóid "
"MeshInstance socraithe go **Statach** sa chigire."

msgid ""
"For imported 3D scenes, the bake mode can be configured in the Import dock "
"after selecting the 3D scene file in the FileSystem dock."
msgstr ""
"Maidir le radhairc 3D allmhairithe, is féidir an modh bácála a chumrú sa "
"duga Iompórtála tar éis an comhad radhairc 3D a roghnú sa duga Comhchórais."

msgid "Add a WorldEnvironment node and create an Environment resource for it."
msgstr "Cuir nód WorldEnvironment leis agus cruthaigh acmhainn Comhshaoil dó."

msgid ""
"Edit the Environment resource, scroll down to the **SDFGI** section and "
"unfold it."
msgstr ""
"Cuir an acmhainn Comhshaoil in eagar, scrollaigh síos go dtí an "
"rannán**SDFGI** agus déan é a oscailt."

msgid ""
"Enable **SDFGI > Enabled**. SDFGI will automatically follow the camera when "
"it moves, so you do not need to configure extents (unlike VoxelGI)."
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh **SDFGI > Cumasaithe**. Leanfaidh SDFGI an ceamara go "
"huathoibríoch nuair a ghluaiseann sé, mar sin ní gá duit méideanna a chumrú "
"(murab ionann agus VoxelGI)."

msgid "Environment SDFGI properties"
msgstr "Airíonna SDFGI comhshaoil"

msgid ""
"In the Environment resource, there are several properties available to "
"adjust SDFGI appearance and quality:"
msgstr ""
"San acmhainn Comhshaoil, tá roinnt airíonna ar fáil chun cuma agus cáilíocht "
"SDFGI a choigeartú:"

msgid ""
"**Use Occlusion:** If enabled, SDFGI will throw additional rays to find and "
"reduce light leaks. This has a performance cost, so only enable this "
"property if you actually need it."
msgstr ""
"** Úsáid Occlusion: ** Má tá sé cumasaithe, caithfidh SDFGI gathanna breise "
"chun sceitheanna solais a aimsiú agus a laghdú. Tá costas feidhmíochta aige "
"seo, mar sin ní chumasaigh an mhaoin seo ach má theastaíonn í uait i "
"ndáiríre."

msgid ""
"**Read Sky Light:** If enabled, the environment lighting is represented in "
"the global illumination. This should be enabled in outdoor scenes and "
"disabled in fully indoor scenes."
msgstr ""
"**Léigh Sky Light:** Má tá sé cumasaithe, léirítear an soilsiú timpeallachta "
"sa soilsiú domhanda. Ba chóir é seo a chumasú i radhairc lasmuigh agus é a "
"dhíchumasú i radhairc go hiomlán laistigh."

msgid ""
"**Bounce Feedback:** By default, indirect lighting only bounces once when "
"using SDFGI. Setting this value above ``0.0`` will cause SDFGI to bounce "
"more than once, which provides more realistic indirect lighting at a small "
"performance cost. Sensible values are usually between ``0.3`` and ``1.0`` "
"depending on the scene. Note that in some scenes, values above ``0.5`` can "
"cause infinite feedback loops to happen, causing the scene to become "
"extremely bright in a few seconds' time. If your indirect lighting looks "
"\"splotchy\", consider increasing this value above ``0.0`` to get more "
"uniform-looking lighting. If your lighting ends up looking too bright as a "
"result, decrease **Energy** to compensate."
msgstr ""
"**Aiseolas Bounce: ** De réir réamhshocraithe, ní bhreabhann soilsiú "
"indíreach ach uair amháin nuair a úsáidtear SDFGI. Má shocraíonn an luach "
"seo os cionn ``0.0`` beidh SDFGI ag preabháil níos mó ná uair amháin, rud a "
"sholáthraíonn soilsiú indíreach níos réalaíoch ar chostas feidhmíochta beag. "
"De ghnáth bíonn luachanna ciallmhar idir ``0.3`` agus ``1.0`` ag brath ar an "
"radharc. Tabhair faoi deara go bhféadfadh luachanna os cionn ``0.5`` lúb "
"aiseolais gan teorainn tarlú i roinnt radhairc, rud a fhágann go mbeidh an "
"radharc thar a bheith geal i gceann cúpla soicind. Má tá cuma “splotach” ar "
"do soilsiú indíreach, smaoinigh ar an luach seo a mhéadú os cionn ``0.0`` "
"chun soilsiú níos aonfhoirmeach a fháil. Má chríochnaíonn do shoilsiú ró-"
"gheal mar thoradh air sin, laghdaigh **Fuinneim** chun cúiteamh a dhéanamh."

msgid ""
"**Cascades:** Higher values result in more detailed GI information (and/or "
"greater maximum distance), but are significantly more expensive on the CPU "
"and GPU. The performance cost of having more cascades especially increases "
"when the camera moves fast, so consider decreasing this to ``4`` or lower if "
"your camera moves fast."
msgstr ""
"**Cascades: ** Mar thoradh ar luachanna níos airde bíonn faisnéis GI níos "
"mionsonraithe (agus/nó an t-achar uasta níos mó), ach tá siad i bhfad níos "
"costasaí ar an LAP agus ar an GPU. Méadaíonn costas feidhmíochta níos mó "
"cascades a bheith agat go háirithe nuair a ghluaiseann an ceamara go tapa, "
"mar sin smaoinigh ar é seo a laghdú go ``4`` nó níos ísle má ghluaiseann do "
"cheamara go tapa."

msgid ""
"**Min Cell Size:** The minimum SDFGI cell size to use for the nearest, most "
"detailed cascade. Lower values result in more accurate indirect lighting and "
"reflection at the cost of lower performance. Adjusting this setting also "
"affects **Cascade 0 Distance** and **Max Distance** automatically."
msgstr ""
"** Íosta Méid na gcille: ** An méid cille SDFGI íosta le húsáid don cascadh "
"is gaire, is mionsonraithe. Mar thoradh ar luachanna níos ísle bíonn soilsiú "
"indíreach agus machnamh níos cruinne ar chostas feidhmíochta níos ísle. "
"Bíonn tionchar ag an socrú seo a choigeartú freisin ar ** Fad Cascade 0** "
"agus **Fad Uas** go huathoibríoch."

msgid ""
"**Cascade 0 Distance:** The distance at which the nearest, most detailed "
"cascade ends. Greater values make the nearest cascade transition less "
"noticeable, at the cost of reducing the level of detail in the nearest "
"cascade. Adjusting this setting also affects **Min Cell Size** and **Max "
"Distance** automatically."
msgstr ""
"**Cascade 0 Fad: ** An fad ag a gcríochnaíonn an cascadh is gaire, is "
"mionsonraithe. Fágann luachanna níos mó an t-aistriú cascadh is gaire nach "
"bhfuil chomh suntasach, ar an gcostas a bhaineann le leibhéal na sonraí sa "
"choscaire is gaire a laghdú Bíonn tionchar ag an socrú seo a choigeartú ar "
"** Méid Cill Mion** agus **Fad Uas** go huathoibríoch."

msgid ""
"**Max Distance:** Controls how far away the signed distance field will be "
"computed (for the least detailed cascade). SDFGI will not have any effect "
"past this distance. This value should always be set below the Camera's Far "
"value, as there is no benefit in computing SDFGI past the viewing distance. "
"Adjusting this setting also affects **Min Cell Size** and **Cascade 0 "
"Distance** automatically."
msgstr ""
"**Fad Uasta: ** Rialaíonn sé cé chomh fada agus ar shiúl a ríomhfar an "
"réimse achair shínithe (don cascadh is lú mionsonraithe). Ní bheidh aon "
"éifeacht ag SDFGI thar an achar seo. Ba chóir an luach seo a shocrú i gcónaí "
"faoi bhun luach Far an Cheamara, mar níl aon tairbhe ann SDFGI a ríomh thar "
"an achar féachana. Bíonn tionchar ag an socrú seo a choigeartú ar **Méid "
"Cill Mion** agus **Fad Cascade 0** go huathoibríoch."

msgid ""
"**Y Scale:** Controls how far apart SDFGI probes are spread *vertically*. By "
"default, vertical spread is the same as horizontal. However, since most game "
"scenes aren't highly vertical, setting the Y Scale to ``75%`` or even "
"``50%`` can provide better quality and reduce light leaks without impacting "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"**Scála Y: ** Rialaíonn sé cé chomh fada agus a scaiptear tábhairí SDFGI* go "
"ingearach*. De réir réamhshocraithe, tá leathadh ingearach mar an gcéanna le "
"cothrománach Mar sin féin, ós rud é nach bhfuil an chuid is mó de radhairc "
"cluiche an-ingearach, is féidir an Scála Y a shocrú go ``75%`` nó fiú "
"``50%`` caighdeán níos fearr a sholáthar agus sceitheanna solais a laghdú "
"gan tionchar a imirt ar fheidhmíocht."

msgid "**Energy:** The brightness multiplier for SDFGI's indirect lighting."
msgstr "**Fuinneamh: ** An iolraitheoir gile do soilsiú indíreach SDFGI."

msgid ""
"**Normal Bias:** The normal bias to use for SDFGI's probe ray bounces. "
"Unlike **Probe Bias**, this only increases the value in relation to the "
"mesh's normals. This makes the bias adjustment more nuanced and avoids "
"increasing the bias too much for no reason. Increase this value if you "
"notice striping artifacts in indirect lighting or reflections."
msgstr ""
"** Gnáthchlaontacht: ** An gnáthchlaonadh atá le húsáid le haghaidh "
"preabhálacha gatha taiscéalaí SDFGI. Murab ionann agus **Probe Bath**, ní "
"mhéadaíonn sé seo ach an luach i ndáil le gnáthmhála na mogalra. Déanann sé "
"seo an coigeartú claonta níos nuasaí agus seachnaíonn sé an claontacht a "
"mhéadú an iomarca gan chúis ar bith. Méadaigh an luach seo má thugann tú "
"faoi deara déantáin striping i soilsiú indíreach nó machnaimh."

msgid ""
"**Probe Bias:** The bias to use for SDFGI's probe ray bounces. Increase this "
"value if you notice striping artifacts in indirect lighting or reflections."
msgstr ""
"**Claonadh Tróibhéil: ** An claonadh atá le húsáid le haghaidh preabhálacha "
"gatha tóibre SDFGI. Méadaigh an luach seo má thugann tú faoi deara déantáin "
"striping i soilsiú indíreach nó machnaimh."

msgid "SDFGI interaction with lights and objects"
msgstr "Idirghníomhaíocht SDFGI le soilse agus rudaí"

msgid ""
"The amount of indirect energy emitted by a light is governed by its color, "
"energy *and* indirect energy properties. To make a specific light emit more "
"or less indirect energy without affecting the amount of direct light emitted "
"by the light, adjust the **Indirect Energy** property in the Light3D "
"inspector."
msgstr ""
"Rialaítear an méid fuinnimh indíreach a astaíonn solas ag a dhath, a "
"fhuinnim* agus* airíonna fuinnimh indíreacha. Chun solas ar leith fuinneamh "
"indíreach níos mó nó níos lú a scaoileadh gan dul i bhfeidhm ar an méid "
"solais dhíreach a astaíonn an solas, coigeartaigh an maoin **Fuinneamh "
"Indíreach sa chigire Light3D."

msgid ""
"To ensure correct visuals when using SDFGI, you must configure your meshes "
"and lights' global illumination properties according to their *purpose* in "
"the scene (static or dynamic)."
msgstr ""
"Chun íomhánna cearta a chinntiú agus SDFGI á úsáid agat, ní mór duit "
"airíonna soilsithe domhanda do mhogalra agus do shoilse a chumrú de réir a "
"g*cuspóir* sa radharc (statach nó dinimiciúil)."

msgid "There are 3 global illumination modes available for meshes:"
msgstr "Tá 3 mhodh soilsithe domhanda ar fáil le haghaidh mogalra:"

msgid ""
"**Disabled:** The mesh won't be taken into account in SDFGI generation. The "
"mesh will receive indirect lighting from the scene, but it will not "
"contribute indirect lighting to the scene."
msgstr ""
"** Míchumas: ** Ní chuirfear an mogalra san áireamh i nginiúint SDFGI. "
"Gheobhaidh an mogalra soilsiú indíreach ón radharc, ach ní chuirfidh sé "
"soilsiú indíreach leis an radharc."

msgid ""
"**Static (default):** The mesh will be taken into account in SDFGI "
"generation. The mesh will both receive *and* contribute indirect lighting to "
"the scene. If the mesh is changed in any way after SDFGI is generated, the "
"camera must move away from the object then move back close to it for SDFGI "
"to regenerate. Alternatively, SDFGI can be toggled off and back on. If "
"neither is done, indirect lighting will look incorrect."
msgstr ""
"** Statach (réamhshocraithe) :** Cuirfear an mogalra san áireamh i nginiúint "
"SDFGI. Gheobhaidh an mogalra* agus* soilsiú indíreach leis an radharc. Má "
"athraítear an mogalra ar bhealach ar bith tar éis SDFGI a ghiniúint, "
"caithfidh an ceamara bogadh ar shiúl ón réad ansin bogadh ar ais gar dó chun "
"SDFGI athghiniúint. De rogha air sin, is féidir SDFGI a chasadh amach agus "
"ar ais. Mura ndéantar ceachtar acu, beidh cuma mícheart ag soilsiú indíreach."

msgid ""
"**Dynamic (not supported with SDFGI):** The mesh won't be taken into account "
"in SDFGI generation. The mesh will receive indirect lighting from the scene, "
"but it will not contribute indirect lighting to the scene. *This acts "
"identical to the **Disabled** bake mode when using SDFGI.*"
msgstr ""
"** Dinimiciúil (nach dtacaítear le SDFGI) :** Ní chuirfear an mogalra san "
"áireamh i nginiúint SDFGI. Gheobhaidh an mogalra soilsiú indíreach ón "
"radharc, ach ní chuirfidh sé soilsiú indíreach leis an radharc. * Feidhmíonn "
"sé seo comhionann leis an modh bácáilte **Díchumasa** agus SDFGI á úsáid "
"agat. *"

msgid ""
"Additionally, there are 3 bake modes available for lights "
"(DirectionalLight3D, OmniLight3D and SpotLight3D):"
msgstr ""
"Ina theannta sin, tá 3 mhodh bácála ar fáil le haghaidh soilse "
"(DirectionalLight3D, OmniLight3D agus Spotlight3D):"

msgid ""
"**Disabled:** The light won't be taken into account for SDFGI baking. The "
"light won't contribute indirect lighting to the scene."
msgstr ""
"**Míchumas: ** Ní chuirfear an solas san áireamh le haghaidh bácáil SDFGI. "
"Ní chuirfidh an solas soilsiú indíreach leis an radharc."

msgid ""
"**Static:** The light will be taken into account for SDFGI baking. The light "
"will contribute indirect lighting to the scene. If the light is changed in "
"any way after baking, indirect lighting will look incorrect until the camera "
"moves away from the light and back (which causes SDFGI to be baked again). "
"will look incorrect. If in doubt, use this mode for level lighting."
msgstr ""
"**Statach: ** Cuirfear an solas san áireamh le haghaidh bácáil SDFGI. "
"Cuirfidh an solas soilsiú indíreach leis an radharc. Má athraítear an solas "
"ar bhealach ar bith tar éis bácáil, beidh cuma mícheart ar an soilsiú "
"indíreach go dtí go mbogann an ceamara ar shiúl ón solas agus ar ais (rud a "
"fhágann go ndéanfar SDFGI a bácáil arís). beidh cuma mícheart. Má tá amhras "
"ort, bain úsáid as an modh seo le haghaidh soilsiú leibhéil."

msgid ""
"**Dynamic (default):** The light won't be taken into account for SDFGI "
"baking, but it will still contribute indirect lighting to the scene in real-"
"time. This option is slower compared to **Static**. Only use the **Dynamic** "
"global illumination mode on lights that will change significantly during "
"gameplay."
msgstr ""
"** Dinimiciúil (réamhshocraithe) :** Ní chuirfear an solas san áireamh le "
"haghaidh bácáil SDFGI, ach cuirfidh sé soilsiú indíreach leis an radharc i "
"bhfíor-am fós. Tá an rogha seo níos moille i gcomparáid len**Statach**. Ná "
"húsáid ach an modh soilsithe domhanda **Dinimic** ar shoilse a athróidh go "
"suntasach le linn gameplay."

msgid ""
"The amount of indirect energy emitted by a light depends on its color, "
"energy *and* indirect energy properties. To make a specific light emit more "
"or less indirect energy without affecting the amount of direct light emitted "
"by the light, adjust the **Indirect Energy** property in the Light3D "
"inspector."
msgstr ""
"Braitheann méid an fhuinnimh indíreach a astaíonn solas ar a dhath, fuinnim* "
"agus* airíonna fuinnimh indíreacha. Chun solas ar leith fuinneamh indíreach "
"níos mó nó níos lú a scaoileadh gan dul i bhfeidhm ar an méid solais "
"dhíreach a astaíonn an solas, coigeartaigh an maoin **Fuinneamh Indíreach sa "
"chigire Light3D."

msgid ""
"See :ref:`doc_introduction_to_global_illumination_gi_mode_recommendations` "
"for general usage recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Féach:ref: `doc_introduction_to_global_illumination_gi_mode_molations` le "
"haghaidh moltaí úsáide ginearálta."

msgid "Adjusting SDFGI performance and quality"
msgstr "Feidhmíocht agus cáilíocht SDFGI a choigeart"

msgid ""
"Since SDFGI is relatively demanding, it will perform best on systems with "
"recent dedicated GPUs. On older dedicated GPUs and integrated graphics, "
"tweaking the settings is necessary to achieve reasonable performance."
msgstr ""
"Ós rud é go bhfuil SDFGI réasúnta éilimh, feidhmeoidh sé is fearr ar chórais "
"a bhfuil GPUanna tiomnaithe le déanaí acu. Ar GPUanna tiomnaithe níos sine "
"agus grafaicí comhtháite, is gá na socruithe a athrú chun feidhmíocht "
"réasúnta a bhaint amach."

msgid ""
"In the Project Settings' **Rendering > Global Illumination** section, SDFGI "
"quality can also be adjusted in several ways:"
msgstr ""
"Sa rannán **Rindreáil > Soilsiú Domhanda** i Socruithe an Tionscadail, is "
"féidir cáilíocht SDFGI a choigeartú ar bhealaí éagsúla freisin:"

msgid ""
"**Sdfgi > Probe Ray Count:** Higher values result in better quality, at the "
"cost of higher GPU usage. If this value is set too low, this can cause "
"surfaces to have visible \"splotches\" of indirect lighting on them due to "
"the number of rays thrown being very low."
msgstr ""
"** Sdfgi > Comhaireamh Probe Ray:** Bíonn cáilíocht níos fearr mar thoradh "
"ar luachanna níos airde, ar chostas úsáide GPU níos airde. Má shocraítear an "
"luach seo ró-íseal, féadann sé seo a bheith ina chúis le dromchlaí "
"“splotches” soilsithe indíreacha a bheith orthu mar gheall ar líon na "
"gathanna a chaitear a bheith an-íseal."

msgid ""
"**Sdfgi > Frames To Converge:** Higher values result in better quality, but "
"GI will take more time to fully converge. The effect of this setting is "
"especially noticeable when first loading a scene, or when lights with a bake "
"mode other than **Disabled** are moving fast. If this value is set too low, "
"this can cause surfaces to have visible \"splotches\" of indirect lighting "
"on them due to the number of rays thrown being very low. If your scene's "
"lighting doesn't have fast-moving lights that contribute to GI, consider "
"setting this to ``30`` to improve quality without impacting performance."
msgstr ""
"**Sdfgi > Frámaí le Cóineasú:** Bíonn cáilíocht níos fearr mar thoradh ar "
"luachanna níos airde, ach tógfaidh sé níos mó ama ar GI teacht le chéile go "
"hiomlán. Tá éifeacht an tsocraithe seo le feiceáil go háirithe agus radharc "
"á luchtú ar dtús, nó nuair a bhíonn soilse le modh bácála seachas "
"**Díchumasaithe** ag gluaiseacht go tapa. Má shocraítear an luach seo ró-"
"íseal, féadann sé seo a bheith ina chúis le dromchlaí “splotches” soilsithe "
"indíreacha a bheith orthu mar gheall ar líon na gathanna a chaitear a bheith "
"an-íseal. Mura bhfuil soilse mearghluaiseachta a chuireann le GI i soilsiú "
"do radharc, smaoinigh ar é seo a shocrú go ``30`` chun cáilíocht a fheabhsú "
"gan cur isteach ar fheidhmíocht."

msgid ""
"**Sdfgi > Frames To Update Light:** Lower values result in moving lights "
"being reflected faster, at the cost of higher GPU usage. If your scene's "
"lighting doesn't have fast-moving lights that contribute to GI, consider "
"setting this to ``16`` to improve performance."
msgstr ""
"** Sdfgi > Frámaí chun Solas a Nuashonrú:** Mar thoradh ar luachanna níos "
"ísle léirítear soilse ag gluaiseacht níos tapúla, ar chostas úsáide GPU níos "
"airde. Mura bhfuil soilse mearghluaiseachta a chuireann le GI i soilsiú do "
"radharc, smaoinigh ar seo a shocrú go ``16`` chun feidhmíocht a fheabhsú."

msgid ""
"**Gi > Use Half Resolution:** If enabled, both SDFGI and VoxelGI will have "
"their GI buffer rendering at halved resolution. For instance, when rendering "
"in 3840×2160, the GI buffer will be computed at a 1920×1080 resolution. "
"Enabling this option saves a lot of GPU time, but it can introduce visible "
"aliasing around thin details."
msgstr ""
"**Gi > Úsáid Leathtaifeach:** Má tá sé cumasaithe, beidh rindreáil maoláin "
"GI SDFGI agus VoxelGI ag taifeach leath. Mar shampla, agus 3840×2160 á "
"rindreáil, déanfar an maolán GI a ríomh ag taifeach 1920×1080. Sábhálann "
"cumasú an rogha seo go leor ama GPU, ach féadann sé ailiasú infheicthe a "
"thabhairt isteach thart ar mhionsonraí tanaí."

msgid ""
"SDFGI rendering performance also depends on the number of cascades and the "
"cell size chosen in the Environment resource (see above)."
msgstr ""
"Braitheann feidhmíocht rindreála SDFGI freisin ar líon na gcascaí agus ar "
"mhéid na gcille a roghnaítear san acmhainn Comhshaoil (féach thuas)."

msgid "SDFGI caveats"
msgstr "Rabhadh SDFGI"

msgid ""
"SDFGI has some downsides due to its cascaded nature. When the camera moves, "
"cascade shifts may be visible in indirect lighting. This can be alleviated "
"by adjusting the cascade size, but also by adding fog (which will make "
"distant cascade shifts less noticeable)."
msgstr ""
"Tá roinnt míbhuntáistí ag SDFGI mar gheall ar a nádúr cascádáilte. Nuair a "
"ghluaiseann an ceamara, d'fhéadfadh go mbeadh aistrithe cascaire le feiceáil "
"i so Is féidir é seo a mhaolú trí mhéid an choscaire a choigeartú, ach "
"freisin trí ceo a chur leis (rud a fhágfaidh go mbeidh athruithe cascadh i "
"gcéin chomh suntasach)."

msgid ""
"Additionally, performance will suffer if the camera moves too fast. This can "
"be fixed in two ways:"
msgstr ""
"Ina theannta sin, beidh feidhmíocht ag fulaingt má bhogann an ceamara ró-"
"tapa. Is féidir é seo a shocrú ar dhá bhealach:"

msgid "Ensuring the camera doesn't move too fast in any given situation."
msgstr "A chinntiú nach mbogann an ceamara ró-thapa in aon chás ar leith."

msgid ""
"Temporarily disabling SDFGI in the Environment resource if the camera needs "
"to be moved at a high speed, then enabling SDFGI once the camera speed slows "
"down."
msgstr ""
"SDFGI a dhíchumasú go sealadach san acmhainn Comhshaoil más gá an ceamara a "
"bhogadh ar luas ard, ansin SDFGI a chumasú nuair a mhoilligh luas an "
"cheamara."

msgid ""
"When SDFGI is enabled, it will also take some time for global illumination "
"to be fully converged (25 frames by default). This can create a noticeable "
"transition effect while GI is still converging. To hide this, you can use a "
"ColorRect node that spans the whole viewport and fade it out when switching "
"scenes using an AnimationPlayer node."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a chumasaítear SDFGI, tógfaidh sé roinnt ama freisin go ndéanfar "
"soilsiú domhanda a chomhcheangal go hiomlán (25 fráma de réir "
"réamhshocraithe). Féadann sé seo éifeacht aistrithe suntasach a chruthú agus "
"GI fós ag teacht le chéile. Chun é seo a cheilt, is féidir leat nód "
"ColorRect a úsáid a chuimsíonn an radharc iomlán agus é a chaitheamh amach "
"agus radhairc á athrú ag baint úsáide as nód AnimationPlayer."

msgid ""
"The signed distance field is only updated when the camera moves in and out "
"of a cascade. This means that if geometry is modified in the distance, the "
"global illumination appearance will be correct once the camera gets closer. "
"However, if a nearby object with a bake mode set to **Static** or "
"**Dynamic** is moved (such as a door), the global illumination will appear "
"incorrect until the camera moves away from the object."
msgstr ""
"Ní dhéantar an réimse achair sínithe a nuashonrú ach nuair a bhogann an "
"ceamara isteach agus amach as cascadh. Ciallaíonn sé seo má dhéantar "
"geoiméadacht a mhodhnú san achar, go mbeidh an chuma soilsithe domhanda "
"ceart nuair a thiocfaidh an ceamara níos gaire. Mar sin féin, má bhogtar "
"réad in aice láimhe le modh bácála atá socraithe u**Statach** nó **Dinimic** "
"(mar shampla doras), beidh an soilsiú domhanda mícheart go dtí go mbogann an "
"ceamara ar shiúl ón réad."

msgid ""
"SDFGI's sharp reflections are only visible on opaque materials. Transparent "
"materials will only use rough reflections, even if the material's roughness "
"is lower than 0.2."
msgstr ""
"Níl machnaimh ghéara SDFGI le feiceáil ach ar ábhair thrédhearcacha. Ní "
"úsáidfidh ábhair thrédhearcacha ach machnaimh garbh, fiú má tá garbh an "
"ábhair níos ísle ná 0.2."
